### Phase 2 — Add SQLite as primary store
Goal: SQLite on NAS holds all payloads + BM25 index. Qdrant kept for vector search only.

### Phase 3 — Fix BBG at full scale (69K rows)
Goal: ingest and retrieve reliably across full dataset.

### Phase 4 — MCP server
Goal: expose retrieval to Claude Desktop via MCP tools.

